revision.text:
&nbsp;
----
This is a [[w:Wikipedia:Redirect|redirect]] from a modification of the target's title; for example, its words are rearranged, or punctuation in the name is changed. In cases of modification from distinctly longer or shorter names, please use {{tl|R from an incomplete name}} or {{tl|R from full name}}.
<includeonly>{{{Category|[[Category:Redirects from modifications]]}}}</includeonly><noinclude>
{{documentation}}
</noinclude>

&nbsp;
----
