&nbsp;
----
This is a [[w:Wikipedia:Redirect|redirect]] from a modification of the target's title; for example, its words are rearranged, or punctuation in the name is changed. In cases of modification from distinctly longer or shorter names, please use {{tl|R from an incomplete name}} or {{tl|R from full name}}.
<includeonly>{{{Category|[[Category:Redirects from modifications]]}}}</includeonly><noinclude>
{{documentation}}
</noinclude>

{{#ifeq:{{{embed}}}|yes
 |{{Redirect template
  |name=From a modification
  |from=a modification of the target's title; for example, its words are rearranged, or punctuation in the name is changed
  |info=In cases of modification from distinctly longer or shorter names, please use {{tl|R from an incomplete name}} or {{tl|R from full name}}.
** Use this Rcat instead of {{tl|R from other capitalisation}} and {{tl|R from plural}} in namespaces other than [[wp:mainspace|mainspace]] for those types of modification.
  |all category=Redirects from modifications
 }}
 |{{Redirect template
  |from=a '''[[:Category:Redirects from modifications|modification]]''' of the target's title; for example, its words are rearranged, or punctuation in the name is changed
  |info=In cases of modification from distinctly longer or shorter names, please use {{tl|R from an incomplete name}} or {{tl|R from full name}}.
** Use this Rcat instead of {{tl|R from other capitalisation}} and {{tl|R from plural}} in namespaces other than [[wp:mainspace|mainspace]] for those types of modification.
<includeonly>
  |all category=Redirects from modifications</includeonly>
 }}
}}<noinclude>
<!-- Categories are to be placed on documentation subpage and interwikis go to Wikidata. -->
{{Documentation}}
<!-- This is template "R from modification" -->
</noinclude>

